-wrap font-display text-4xl font-medium leading-[1.08] tracking-tight md:text-6xl\"><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Builds</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">AI</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">systems</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">for</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">critical</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">infrastructure</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">that</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">have</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">to</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">be</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">right,</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">not</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">just</span><span class=\"mr-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">fast.</span></h1><p class=\"mt-6 max-w-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-fg-muted md:text-lg\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)\">Parth designs and ships production-grade AI systems for infrastructure-critical domains — currently building RailMind, an AI-powered railway infrastructure management platform.</p><div class=\"mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(12px)\"><div class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:none\"><a class=\"focus-ring inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-sm px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-150 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent to-accent2 text-white shadow-lg hover:opacity-90 hover:shadow-accent/30 hover:shadow-xl transition-all\" href=\"/work\">View work</a></div><div class=\"inline-block\" style=\"transform:none\"><a class=\"focus-ring inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-sm px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-150 bg-bg-elevated text-fg border border-border hover:border-accent/50 hover:bg-bg-inset\" href=\"/resume.pdf\">Download resume</a></div></div></div><div class=\"hidden md:flex md:items-center md:justify-center\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:scale(0.95)\"><div class=\"relative\"><div class=\"absolute -inset-4 rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/30 via-accent2/20 to-transparent blur-2xl\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></div><div class=\"relative rounded-3xl p-[2px] bg-gradient-to-br from-accent via-accent2 to-accent/40\"><div class=\"overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-bg-inset w-[260px] h-[340px]\"><img alt=\"Professional photo\" width=\"896\" height=\"1196\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover object-[center_8%]\" style=\"color:transparent\" src=\"/Profile.png\"/></div></div><span class=\"absolute -bottom-2 -right-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-accent to-accent2 shadow-lg shadow-accent/50\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span><span class=\"absolute -top-2 -left-2 h-2.5 w-2.5 rounded-full bg-accent2/70\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span></div></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-content px-6 py-10\"><div class=\"track-rule mb-8\"></div><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 font-mono text-sm text-fg-muted md:flex-row md:gap-10\"><span class=\"text-fg-subtle\">NOW /</span><span>building <span class=\"text-fg\">RailMind — production hardening and demo rollout</span></span><span class=\"text-fg-subtle\">·</span><span>learning <span class=\"text-fg\">[Currently learning]</span></span><span class=\"ml-auto text-fg-subtle\">updated <!-- -->2026-07</span></div></div></section><section class=\"mx-auto max-w-content px-6 py-16\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div class=\"mb-8 flex items-end justify-between\"><h2 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-medium md:text-3xl\">Featured work</h2><a class=\"focus-ring inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-sm px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium transition-colors duration-150 text-fg-muted hover:text-fg hover:bg-bg-inset\" href=\"/work\">All projects →</a></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-6\"><div style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(24px)\"><div style=\"transform:perspective(800px)\"><div class=\"rounded-md border border-border p-6 transition-all duration-300 hover:border-accent/40 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-accent/10 glass flex flex-col gap-5\"><div class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-4\"><div><a class=\"focus-ring\" href=\"/work/railmind\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-2xl font-medium hover:text-accent transition-colors\">RailMind</h3></a><p class=\"mt-2 max-w-lg text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-muted\">Production-grade AI platform for railway infrastructure management — signal risk, asset health, and maintenance ops in one system.</p></div><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-sm px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono tracking-wide bg-signal-green/10 text-signal-green\">active</span></div><p class=\"border-l-2 border-accent/30 pl-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-subtle\">Railway infrastructure teams operate on siloed, reactive tooling — asset state, signal risk, and maintenance history live in disconnected systems, so failures get diagnosed after the fact instead of predicted before it.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 md:grid-cols-4\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1 border-l-2 border-border pl-3\"><span class=\"font-mono text-2xl font-medium text-fg font-tabular\">9.7 / 10</span><span class=\"text-xs text-fg-subtle uppercase tracking-wider\">Production readiness</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1 border-l-2 border-border pl-3\"><span class=\"font-mono text-2xl font-medium text-fg font-tabular\">58</span><span class=\"text-xs text-fg-subtle uppercase tracking-wider\">API routes audited</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1 border-l-2 border-border pl-3\"><span class=\"font-mono text-2xl font-medium text-fg font-tabular\">232</span><span class=\"text-xs text-fg-subtle uppercase tracking-wider\">Files in final build</span></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1 border-l-2 border-border pl-3\"><span class=\"font-mono text-2xl font-medium text-fg font-tabular\">6</span><span class=\"text-xs text-fg-subtle uppercase tracking-wider\">Audit phases</span></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-sm px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono tracking-wide bg-bg-inset text-fg-muted\">Next.js 14</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-sm px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono tracking-wide bg-bg-inset text-fg-muted\">NestJS 10</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-sm px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono tracking-wide bg-bg-inset text-fg-muted\">LangGraph</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-sm px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono tracking-wide bg-bg-inset text-fg-muted\">PostgreSQL</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-sm px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono tracking-wide bg-bg-inset text-fg-muted\">Neo4j</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-sm px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono tracking-wide bg-bg-inset text-fg-muted\">Qdrant</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-sm px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono tracking-wide bg-bg-inset text-fg-muted\">Redis</span><span class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 rounded-sm px-2 py-1 text-xs font-mono tracking-wide bg-bg-inset text-fg-muted\">Turborepo</span></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 pt-1 text-sm\"><a class=\"focus-ring text-accent hover:text-accent2 transition-colors hover:underline\" href=\"/work/railmind\">Case study →</a><a href=\"#\" class=\"focus-ring text-accent hover:text-accent2 transition-colors hover:underline\">System docs<!-- --> →</a><a h